title: PF RoIO
description:
Select Pink Floyd Bootlegs from throughout their career:

1969 - Green is the Coulour
1971 - Pompeii
1972 - Dark Side of the Sky
1972 - Horizons
1973 - Yeeskul
1975 - Holes in they Sky
1977 - Oakland
1977 - Azimuth Coordinator Part 2 Quebec
1980 - The Wall live
CD Full of Secrets
Total Eclipse - A complete Pink Floyd Retrospective (4 CDs)

Details of all shows can be found in the Pink Floyd RoIO database (just Google it)

Enjoy. I don't know if these are the best Floyd audience recordings around, but they are the best of my collection.
